snippet.textDisplay:
kea mojoda halaat me wohe tehreek phir nahi shro kr dene chahea jo 1400 saal pehle Muhammad sallal laho alaihe wassallam ne shro ke the ku ke us me sirf aek akele Allah se mangne aur us ko haqiqee khaliq ,malik aur raaziq manne ke baat ke gae the aur  mushrikeen Makkah jo iss baat ko mante the leken saath me izafa iss baat se krte the majaze khaliq,maliq aur raziq nabio aur walio ko bhe mante the aur un se ghebi madad mang kr Quran ki iss ayat ka inkaar krte the iyyak nabodo wa iyyak nastaeen  matlab ae Allah hum tere he ibadat krte he aur tujh he se madad mangte he 
aaj kal bhe brelvi aur shia jumaate musalmano ka roop dhaar ker yehe concept jo hindio ka he us ke talimaat ko ubhaar rahe he Allah apne khaliq malik raaziq hone me aek he akela he aur koi nabi aur koi wali us ke ninawe siffat me us ke saath shreek nahi aur majazan bhe shreek nahi 
sifarish sirf aek nabi ka haq he aur wo hmarare akhri nabi Muhammad bin Abdullah sallal laho alaihe wassalam  ka haq he aur wo bhe qayyamat ke din un ko mile ga jab koi ghebi kalimaat un ko sekhae jae ge jin ko wo abhe tak nahi jante iss lea sabit hua ke kuch ghebi ilm Allah ne akhri nabi se bhe chupa kr rakha he beshak Allah he haqiqee ilm gheb rakhte he aur nabi jo ilm ke behr be karan he leken Allah ke muqable me un ke ilm ki misaal sumandar me qatre ke braber nahi

jab sifarish sirf nabi kareem Muhammad bin Abdullah kr sakte he aur nabi bhe nahi kr sakte to phir brelvi aur shia ku qabro per qabar wale ko sifarshi maan kr ghebi mada ke lea pukaarte he blke masjido me bhe ghebi mada peeran peer aur hussain razi allah se mang rahe hote he 
             ye do kkome nazriye ke blkul khilaaf he jis ko aap anchors ne khatam krna he mere khyal me sirf do minute lagte he ye baat krne me aap ke baar baar duhrane se in sha  Allah bohat faraq pare ga aur hum sahe imman o yaqeen ke saath hindu essai yahood aur kufaar munafiqeen se larne ke qabil ho jae ge aur asbaab ke na hote hue bhe fatah hmari ho ge
          Allah apko aur apke bacho ko aur mujhe do kome nazriye ke mojoda taqazo ko samajhne ke tofeeq de
